al concerns at stake.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aEmotions (Philosophy) 0aEmotions (Philosophy). 0aSenses and sensation. 4aEnvironmental Studies : Ecology. 4aEnvironmental Studies : Environmental Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Ancient Greek Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Continental Philosophy. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143847862340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438478623423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438478623/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles